    "BLIP-2 15 is a pre-training strategy that bootstraps vision-language pre-training from off-the-shelf frozen pre-trained image encoders and frozen large language models.",
    "We utilized their off-shelf checkpoint for zero-shot evaluation.",
    "Pre-trained backbones.",
    "In this section, we introduce the pre-trained models used in our experiments.",
    "We separate them into language and vision backbones."
